be optimistic in a time of difficulties" in order to accomplish
economic adjustment.
</P>
<P>
In the afternoon, children came with their parents to the
carnival to enjoy themselves in various amusement games despite
the rain. While playing the games and tasting their favorite
snacks, the crowd had a chance to listen to some well-known songs
and marches from China's inland areas with such theme as
"Five-star red flag (China's national flag) flies in the wind."
</P>
<P>
