<HEADLINE> Doohan Takes Dutch GP Pole Position </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, June 26 (Xinhau) -- Four times world champion Michael
Doohan of Australia took the pole position for Saturday's Dutch
500cc motorcycling Grand Prix in Assen, Netherlands after winning
Friday's final practice.
